  "keyFeatures": [
    "AI-powered semantic matching with vector embeddings",
    "Multi-channel feedback capture (Slack, web UI, forms)",
    "Intelligent triaging with three-tier confidence system",
    "Human-in-the-loop approval workflows via Slack",
    "Area insights generation with AI agents",
    "Durable workflow execution with Workflow DevKit",
